on-changes.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/gwent-the-witcher-card-game-allowing-players-to-vote-on-changes-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/gwent-the-witcher-card-game-allowing-players-to-vote-on-changes-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/gwent-the-witcher-card-game-allowing-players-to-vote-on-changes-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/gwent-the-witcher-card-game-allowing-players-to-vote-on-changes-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/gwent-the-witcher-card-game-allowing-players-to-vote-on-changes-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/gwent">《昆特牌</a>：巫师卡牌游戏》</em>将把游戏的未来交到玩家手中，因为<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/cd-projekt-red">CD Projekt Red</a>在 11.10 更新后不再推出更改。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/boss-level-2023-bryan-intihar-marvels-spider-man-2-3516664">Bryan Intihar 如何在《漫威蜘蛛侠 2》中打造电子游戏杰作</a></strong></li></ul><p>“这是<em>《昆特牌》</em> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/cd-projekt-red-plans-to-end-active-development-on-gwent-after-2023-3360833">最后一次由开发者手工制作的内容更新</a>，”设计师 Moleigon 在发布到游戏官方 YouTube 频道的视频中谈到 11.10 更新时说道。看看下面： </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="昆特牌：巫师卡牌游戏 |更新 11.10 概述" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/qMxDjGoKtQ4?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “所以此后我们将不再准备对卡牌进行更改。相反，我们将使用一个系统，你可以在主菜单中看到它，它被称为平衡委员会，”他们继续说道。</p><p>只有拥有一级声望且处于职业排名或在<em>昆特牌</em>当前赛季赢得 25 场排名赛的玩家才能在平衡委员会中投票。</p><p>通过将卡牌放入特定的括号中，他们将决定补给的成本和卡牌的威力。将卡片放入最高括号算作三票，中括号算两票，底括号算一票。</p><p>如果玩家愿意，他们可以将同一张<em>昆特</em>牌放在多个括号中，即使效果相互抵消，但最终只会实施最受欢迎的更改。 </p><figure id="attachment_3517100" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3517100" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3517100" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/gwent-the-witcher-card-game-allowing-players-to-vote-on-changes-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/gwent-the-witcher-card-game-allowing-players-to-vote-on-changes-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/gwent-the-witcher-card-game-allowing-players-to-vote-on-changes-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/gwent-the-witcher-card-game-allowing-players-to-vote-on-changes-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/gwent-the-witcher-card-game-allowing-players-to-vote-on-changes-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/gwent-the-witcher-card-game-allowing-players-to-vote-on-changes-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/gwent-the-witcher-card-game-allowing-players-to-vote-on-changes-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3517100" class="wp-caption-text"> 《昆特牌：巫师卡牌游戏》图片来源：CD Projekt Red</figcaption></figure><p>投票将每月举行一次，不过，11 月将进行两次投票，以便 CD Projekt Red 可以判断新方法是否成功。</p><p> “我们希望参与平衡委员会的人主要是熟悉当前版本的经验丰富的玩家；然而，我们也希望为排名较低的玩家提供代表的机会，只要他们在当前赛季中保持活跃，”开发者在有关平衡委员会的<a href="https://www.playgwent.com/en/news/49294/balance-council-faq-what-is-it-how-to-use-it" target="_blank" rel="noopener">常见问题</a>中解释道。</p><p>去年，有消息称<em>《昆特牌</em>》的游戏总监<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/gwent-head-jason-slama-is-the-next-witcher-titles-game-director-3187742">Jason Slama 将负责推动下一款<em>《巫师》</em>游戏的开发</a>。</p><p>话虽如此，3 月份 Pixelcraft Studios 宣布聘请 Slama 担任<em>Gotchi Guardians</em>的总监，这是一款使用“区块链游戏，同时打破传统可访问性障碍并突破 Web3 游戏质量界限的塔防游戏”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3517101" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3517101" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full w